Foxwedge Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















foxwedge inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Consumer Electronics
Foxwedge, Inc. produces interactive multimedia software, including High Definition Audio (HDA) systems. The Company's products are designed to be used in home and automobile stereo systems, video cassette recorders and professional and commercial audio equipment.




