Meredith Heron's Modern Gatsby for DXV loo
19/25



                    Honey, make me a gin gimlet and get in here!" (Holler that in your best Mae West voice.) Designer Meredith Heron heralds in the Golden Age with this dashing Modern Gatsby bathroom. The loo is tricked out in luxurious DXV by American Standard fixings. The room makes you want to plunk in the tub with a pal and a cocktail. Favourites: the edgy Deco floors, the deep blue-greys,  the fireplace screens and that divine gilded chandelier
                



